# BackTrace
## 1. 子集型
```cpp
//输入
int n; cin >> n
vector<int> a(n);
for(int& i : a) cin >> a;
```
### (1) Choose Or Not
```cpp
//生成所有子集
vector<vector<int> ans;
vector<int> path;

auto dfs = [&](this auto&& dfs, int i) -> void
{
	if(i == n)
	{
		ans.emplace_back(path);
		return;
	}

	dfs(i + 1);

	path.push_back(a[i]);
	dfs(i + 1);
	path.pop_back();
};
dfs(0);

```
### (2) Enumerate Answer
```cpp
vector<vector<int> ans;
vector<int> path;

auto dfs = [&](this auto&& dfs, int i) -> void
{
	ans.emplace_back(path);

	for(int j = i; j < n; j++)
	{
		path.push_back(a[j]);
		dfs(j + 1);
		path.pop_back();
	}
};
dfs(0);
```

